      </accessrestrict>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_61e07e7d4a356310a25cdf3ba0018b00">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records of the Yale University Tribunal contain correspondence, transcripts and court records related to a case before the University Tribunal.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
